  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Structural separation:</strong> Helps assistive technologies distinguish data from headers and footers</li>
      <li><strong>Implicit role:</strong> tbody has an implicit ARIA role of <code>rowgroup</code></li>
      <li><strong>Row headers:</strong> When rows have their own headers, use <a href="/docs/elements/native/th/"><code>&lt;th scope="row"&gt;</code></a> in the first cell</li>
      <li><strong>Row navigation:</strong> Screen readers can navigate between different table sections (thead, tbody, tfoot)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

